44JRirK3sPU.title: Mass Effect 2 Music Video - Stay With Me (Ashley & Shepard)
44JRirK3sPU.description:
Hi to everyone! I've finally found new video footage for my videos and this one is dedicated to Ashley Williams & John Shepard (romance).  First, I have to thank Philip (DJBACON8D) for his gameplay. He allowed me to use his gameplay of the game and thanks to him I could make this video. I put the link for his Youtube channel even in this video description, at the bottom of the screen (after gametrailers.com link). Thanks again! ^_^
Ashley is my favorite female character in Mass Effect and when I play with my brother to the first ME (he play always with MaleShepard), he always romanced her (and I'm agree fully with him). I like Ashley for various reasons and think she is one of the best female character in this awesome game. I also like Kasumi, Liara, Miranda and Tali, but Ashley is really special for me. 
The video starts with Shepard's awakening and following there are all moments with Ash and John together in ME1. Shepard thinks back to times he had with the woman he loves, with the battle against Saren and Geth. When he wakes up many things have changed: now there's Cerberus, The Illusive Man and Miranda. Miranda considers important Shepard for the suicide mission, but she could also be a rival in love for Ashley. Ashley still loves Shepard, but decided not to join his team because of the presence of Cerberus. The mission has priority, but Shepard thinks of her before throwing in the suicide mission. He still loves her and perhaps after the suicide mission, Shepard and Ash will be together again. These are my hopes! :)
I dedicate this video to all Ashley's fans (and me too). I think this song works really well for this theme. :) Hope you like it! ^_^

A very special thanks to my dear friends Bryan, who helped me to choose the song, Philip (DJBACON8D), who helped me with his gameplay, Danny (rhysh1), my brother Fabio, Alessandro, Alfredo, Lanfranco, Mary & Danny, all my subscribers on Youtube channel, all friends in my town, all those who love Mass Effect (like you and me), Buggirl, Alexine, and all friends of the Clan V (legendary group of Garrus Thread), Vrex360 and all Ashley Thread, and Forum by Bioware. THANKS TO EVERYONE!!!!

Watch the video, comment and subscribe to my channel. STAY TUNED! :)

Aqualung performed live by Jethro Tull live at the Hippodrome in London on February of 1977

The Minstrel Looks Back 1969-1977 2-DVD set
This 2-DVD set includes:
- Live in Tampa, Fl, July 31, 1976
- Live at the London Hippodrome, Feb. 10, 1977
- Live at the Tanglewood Music Fair, July 7, 1970
- An appearance on German TV, 1970
- Appearances from Swedish TV, 1969
- Rare mint quality footage of promotional videos for A Witches Promise and Teacher originally broadcast on French TV in 1970

Rare promotional videos for:
- Bouree, 1969
- Life's A Long Song, 1971
- Living in the Past, 1976
- Too Old to Rock n Roll, Too Young to Die, 1976
- The Whistler, 1977
- A full clip of "The Minstrel in the Gallery" from a never released show filmed in Paris in November of 1975!
- Rare 8mm clips of performances from A Passion Play and Thick as a Brick tours. Both of which were never professionally recorded in either video or audio. Amazing, right?
- The original film of "The Hare Who Lost His Spectacles" that was shown during the Passion Play concerts

www.myspace.com/tommygunvideo

- This Was, 1968
- Stand Up, 1969
- Benefit, 1970
- Aqualung, 1971
- Living in the Past, 1972
- Thick as a Brick, 1972
- A Passion Play, 1973
- Warchild, 1974
- Minstrel in the Gallery, 1975
- Too Old to Rock n Roll, Too Young to Die, 1976
- Songs From the Wood

If you are new to Jethro Tull and have enjoyed watching all the progressive rock clips that you see on youtube I suggest that you go out and buy these CDs. They are from Jethro Tull's prime and I think you would enjoy them.

L3bVtpVKC0o.title: PATRIOTIC Chocolate Covered Homestyle Pretzels w/ Sprinkles - Learn how to make
L3bVtpVKC0o.description:
Celebrate the 4TH OF JULY with "White Chocolate Covered Homestyle Pretzels w/ Red, White & Blue Sprinkles". A perfect simply and easy delicious treat that most everyone will enjoy!! Click on "Show more" below to get recipe...

PATRIOTIC White Chocolate Covered HOMESTYLE PRETZELS

16 homestyle PRETZELS, medium size
2 ounces white chocolate, 1/2 white chocolate chip may be used
Red, White & Blue sprinkles

Add pretzels to wax paper in a single layer.

Melt chocolate over double boiler or in microwave, stirring every 15 seconds, until melted.

With spoon, drizzle melted chocolate over pretzels. 

Add sprinkles.

Chocolate will become solid after 30 minutes.  Add to refrigerator for 15 minutes or freezer 5 minutes to set chocolate faster.

Serve and ENJOY!!!
keywords: How to make chocolate covered Pretzels
How to make chocolate covered Pretzels with Sprinkles

b5dscR40aPY.title: VW Touareg 3.0 V6 BlueMotion - Preview
b5dscR40aPY.description:
Fahrzeugvorstellung: VW Touareg - Der Nomade unter den Offroadern

Am Anfang seiner Karriere macht der VW Touareg vor allem durch seine erfolgreiche Teilnahme an der Dakar von sich reden. VW bietet ganze 15 Ausstattungsversionen und 5 verschiedene Motorisierungen, inklusive einer Hybridversion. Permanenter Allrad, Wattiefe von bis zu 580 mm und hohe Werte für Böschungswinkel, Querneigung und Rampenwinkel machen den Straßennomaden Offroad-tauglich. Ein Steigungswinkel von 45° plus Berganfahrassistent lassen das Gefährt vor kaum einem Hindernis zurückschrecken. Drei Dieselmotoren, ein Benziner und ein Hybridantrieb bringen den 2,1 Tonnen schweren Brocken (Leergewicht) in weniger als 10 Sekunden auf 100 km/h und je nach Motor auf 228 km/h Höchstgeschwindigkeit. Alle Modelle verfügen über eine 8-Gang-Automatik. Vollgestopft mit diversen Assistenzsystemen wie der automatischen Distanzregelung, dem Side-, Rear-, Lane- und Dynamic Light Assist oder der Parkhilfe ist der Touareg auch auf der Straße sicher. Als Sondereditionen bietet VW den Offroader als R-Linie und als exklusive Edition X. Preislich beginnt der Geländespaß aus Wolfsburg bei rund 50.000 Euro, nach oben lassen sich aber auch lässig fast 100.000 Euro erreichen.
